text: Allophylus rhomboidalis is a species of plant in the family Sapindaceae. It is found in French Polynesia and Pitcairn. ==See also== *Flora of Tubuai ==References== rhomboidalis Category:Flora of the Pitcairn Islands Category:Flora of the Tubuai Islands Category:Least concern plants Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
